OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FIn the Australian Outback when the
OL,7,     Fgoing gets tough the tough drive
OL,8,     Ftrucks. Outback truckers drive the
OL,9,     Fbiggest trucks on Earth along the
OL,10,     Ftoughest roads and loneliest
OL,11,     Fhighways.
OL,12,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,13,     FThere's an emergency in
OL,14,     FNottinghamshire when the ground
OL,15,     Fgives way beneath a tipper truck
OL,16,     Ffully loaded with stone aggregate.
OL,17,     FIn Middlesbrough, a bus gets
OL,18,     Fgrounded on a grassy verge.
